                     <interp inst="t18300916-284-person2361" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was on duty - I got this shift from the boy.</p>
               <p>Prisoners' Defence (written). I and my brother went with another girl to the shop to pledge some articles, and whilst I was in the shop the girl gave my brother a shift to hold; soon after Mr. Matthews sent for an officer, and gave us in charge.</p>

